reviewText: I have watched this DVD over and over again.  I still cannot believe the type of stuff going on in here.  Crazy people out there son.  I highly recommend you check it out.
I love this stuff.  Crazy ghetto action from start to finish.  Thank the lord I don't live in this town.
What can i say about this dvd except that it sucks. Maybe one or two good fights other than that a lot of poor camera work and boring fights.
